snippet.title: Prime Mom
snippet.description:
Pregnancy, Motherhood, Vlogs
This channel is created for people who are stepping into the beautiful world of pregnancy, or are preparing to embark on this journey. Prime Mom is mainly targeted for New mothers as it captures experiences of an Indian mother in this beautiful journey of pregnancy.
